unittitle_ssm: Rope Makers' Benevolent Society of Brooklyn record book
abstract_ssm: This collection consists of one record book containing the printed articles of incorporation and rules and regulations of the Rope Makers' Benevolent Society of Brooklyn, as well as a handwritten roll of members.  Also included are a photographic negative and print of a cloth emblem of the Society.
